e%20wake%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThe%20necessary%20balance%20between%20fashion%20and%20exclusivity%2C%20which%20supports%20the%20house%20ability%20to%20attract%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20consumers%2C%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20diluted.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20for%20BI%20for%20this%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGucci's%20pace%20of%20growth%20was%20unsustainable%2C%20even%20without%20current%20macroeconomic%20headwinds%2C%20and%20the%20strategy%20behind%20the%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20embracing%20a%20singular%20trend%20across%20all%20product%20verticals%2C%20appealing%20to%20aspirational%20customers%2C%20and%20relying%20heavily%20on%20China%20%E2%80%94%20was%20never%20going%20to%20have%20lasting%20success%2C%20fashion%20pros%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20did%20too%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Jelena%20Sokolova%2C%20a%20senior%20equity%20analyst%20at%20Morningstar%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20logomania%20to%20logo%20fatigue.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Alessandro%20Michele%20design%20is%20easy%20to%20pick%20out%20of%20a%20lineup%3A%20They%20tend%20to%20be%20ornate%20and%20flowery%2C%20and%20feature%20the%20brand's%20classic%20double%20Gs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLogomania%2C%26quot%3B%20publicist%20Solomon%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20most%20influential%20brand%20in%20fashion%20in%20terms%20of%20maximalism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Michele's%20first%20collection%20hit%2C%20it%20flew%20off%20the%20shelves%2C%20igniting%20the%20brand's%20massive%20growth.%20As%20BI%20declared%20at%20the%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkering-and-gucci-2015-financial-results-sales-income-outlook-2016-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGucci%20was%20cool%20again.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223712%5C%2