C%20sustainability%20%E2%80%94%20something%20to%20push%20the%20conversation%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20embrace%20of%20a%20singular%20aesthetic%2C%20which%20was%20great%20for%20creating%20a%20unified%2C%20strong%20brand%2C%20proved%20less%20ideal%20when%20it%20was%20out%20of%20style.%20It%20all%20started%20to%20seem%20a%20little%20gimmicky%2C%20and%20without%20any%20diversification%2C%20there%20were%20few%20products%20for%20customers%20to%20gravitate%20toward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20something%20that%20some%20predicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20still%20believe%20the%20Gucci%20brand's%20current%20growth%20rate%2C%20which%20is%2010%20times%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20the%20industry%2C%20represents%20a%20risk%20going%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Morningstar's%20Sokolova%20wrote%20in%20a%202017%20note.%20%26quot%3BWe%20prefer%20to%20take%20a%20prudent%20stance%20and%20acknowledge%20market%20saturation%20risk%2C%20given%20the%20very%20distinct%20aesthetics%20of%20the%20current%20collections%20(which%20can%20produce%20both%20tremendous%20demand%20uptick%20and%20fatigue).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20great%20gamble%20of%20Michele's%20Gucci%2C%20which%20had%20paid%20off%20for%20years%2C%20was%20starting%20to%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20luxe%20can%20a%20brand%20be%20in%20the%20metaverse%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Gucci's%20fate%20wasn't%20all%20tied%20up%20in%20its%20designs.%20Macroeconomic%20conditions%20had%20just%20as%20big%20of%20an%20effect%20on%20its%20sales%20as%20its%20aesthetics%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%20height%2C%20the%20brand%20not%20only%20embraced%20maximalism%20in%20its%20designs%20but%20also%20in%20its%20partnerships%3A%20The%20North%20Face%2C%20Disney%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fgucci-sandbox-metaverse-land-ethereum-roblox-nft-crypto-vault-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20metaverse%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gucci%20x%20Disney%20bag%20before%20Cecile%20Bahnsen%20on%20January%2029%2C%202020%20in%20Copenhagen%2C%20Denmark.%20(Photo%20by%20Jeremy%20Moeller%2FGetty%20Images)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633c3280dfb1341e901e515%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGucci's%20collections%20with%20Disney%20and%20North%20Face%20may%20have%20been%20a%20hit%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20they%20diminished%20the%20brand's%20value.%3Cp%3EJeremy%20Moeller%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20these%20mass-market%20partnerships%20and%20the%20trend-driven%20nature%20of%20Michele's%20looks%2C%20Gucci%20gained%20a%20wide%20following%2C%20particularly%20among%20younger%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flvmh-says-the-aspirational-customer-is-suffering-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20aspirational%20%E2%80%94%20or%20less%20wealthy%20%E2%80%94%20customers.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20different%20approach%20than%20at%20Herm%C3%A8s%2C%20which%20embraces%20high%20cost%20and%20scarcity%20to%20fuel%20growth.%20And%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20it%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20plus%2C%20as%20it%20exposed%20the%20brand%20to%20a%20new%20audience%20that%20didn't%20traditionally%20buy%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Gucci%20developed%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20dependence%26quot%3B%20on%20those%20consumers%2C%20Chauvet%20said%2C%20and%20as%20economic%20uncertainty%20and%20inflation%20grew%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20they%20blew%20through%20their%20pandemic%20savings%20%E2%80%94%20those%20customers%20became%20the%20first%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApart%20from%20the%20ultra-ultrawealthy%2C%20we%20are%20all%20feeling%20the%20cost-of-living%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20Roberts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20save%20money%2C%20aspirational%20customers%20are%20turning%20more%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhermes-gen-z-resale-birkin-bag-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresale%20sites%2C%20where%20they%20can%20get%20luxury%20products%20for%20less%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20plus%20a%20little%20wear%20and%20tear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20200%20double-G%20logo%20Gucci%20belts%20were%20available%20on%20luxury%20consignment%20shop%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fthe-real-real-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20RealReal%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20as%20little%20as%20%24208.%20Online%2C%20the%20most%20simple%20version%20of%20the%20belt%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20became%20a%20staple%20of%20Michele's%20Gucci%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0cost%20%24520.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20younger%20customers%20who%20can%20still%20afford%20to%20splurge%20may%20simply%20not%20want%20to%20spend%20on%20such%20flashy%20items%20or%20have%20moved%20on%20to%20different%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20consumers%20that%20were%20buying%20Gucci%20at%20its%20height%2C%20they%20are%20getting%20older%2C%26quot%3B%20Roberts%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20may%20not%20want%20to%20be%20walking%20around%20with%20big%20logos.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Chinese%20boom%20turned%20bust.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Gucci%20was%20a%20chart-topper%20with%20aspirational%20consumers%20in%20traditional%20luxury%20markets%2C%20it%20went%20multiplatinum%20in%20China.%20The%20Asia-Pacific%20region%2C%20fueled%20by%20China%2C%20grew%20from%20representing%2035%25%20of%20the%20label's%20sales%20in%202015%20to%2044%25%20in%202021.%20Revenue%20in%20the%20region%20tripled%20in%20that%20period%2C%20outpacing%20total%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224952%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Customers%20enter%20a%20Gucci%20store%20at%20Sanya%20International%20Duty%20Free%20Shopping%20Complex%20on%20June%2028%2C%202023%20in%20Sanya%2C%20Hainan%20Province%20of%20China.%20(Photo%20by%20Jiang%20Qiming%2FChina%20News%20Service%2FVCG%20via%20Getty%20Images)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633bb6a10dfcda40965fb65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223301%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGucci%20relied%20heavily%20on%20China%20for%20its%20growth%2C%20but%20stores%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0perhaps%20including%20this%20one%20in%20China's%20Hainan%20Province%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0have%20struggled%20recently.%3Cp%3EChina%20News%20Service%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20great%20while%20Chinese%20shoppers%20were%20spending%20money%2C%20but%20as%20they%20reined%20that%20in%2C%20Gucci%20slumped.%20Just%20as%20Gucci%20relied%20too%20heavily%20on%20one%20designer%20and%20on%20aspirational%20consumers%2C%20it%20relied%20too%20heavily%20on%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20pandemic%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-luxury-market-comeback-pandemic-bofa-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxury%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%20never%20rebounded%20as%20expected%2C%20and%20the%20country's%20economic%20growth%20slowed%20and%20consumers%20remained%20cautious.%20China's%20luxury%20market%20tripled%20between%202017%20and%202021%2C%20but%20despite%20growth%20last%20year%2C%20it%20has%20slowed%20since%202021%2C%20according%20to%20research%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bain.com%2Finsights%2F2023-china-luxury-goods-market%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%25202023%252C%2520Chinese%2520luxury%2520consumption%2C%2525%2520(both%2520excluding%2520Daigou).%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBain%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20foreign%20travel%20still%20down%20among%20Chinese%20people%2C%20they%20are%20not%20spending%20abroad%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20scale%2C%20brands%20are%20missing%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Roberts%20said%20of%20the%20Chinese%20consumer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20the%20label's%20target%20demo%20within%20the%20country%20was%20still%20aspirational%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20a%20double%20blow.%20Like%20in%20other%20markets%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-rich-go-for-quiet-luxury-stealth-wealth-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eultrawealthy%20in%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20still%20are%20spending%20are%20favoring%20brands%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhermes-bag-collectors-birkin-kelly-purse-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHerm%C3%A8s%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Chanel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20Gucci's%20first-quarter%20sales%20in%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20region%2C%20which%20is%20fueled%20by%20China%2C%20fell%2028%25%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20the%20year%20prior.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20brand's%20sales%20in%20the%20region%20grew%20just%205%25%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20double-digit%20expansion%20it%20had%20been%20experiencing%20in%20its%20heyday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20context%20right%20now%20is%20not%20supportive%20because%20it%20is%20more%20polarized%2C%26quot%3B%20Armelle%20Poulou%2C%20Kering's%20chief%20financial%20officer%2C%20said%20about%20China%20during%20an%20earnings%20call%20last%20month.%20%26quot%3BGucci%20at%20the%20moment%20is%20not%20in%20the%20sweet%20spot%20in%20terms%20of%20positioning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20not%20all%20over%20for%20the%20House%20of%20Gucci.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20looks%20like%20Gucci%20and%20its%20new%20creative%20director%2C%20De%20Sarno%2C%20have%20their%20work%20cut%20out%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20the%20end%20of%20the%20label.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20probably%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20such%20a%20big%20deal%20if%20Gucci%20hadn't%20had%20such%20a%20legacy%20of%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20never%20leave%20the%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20Solomon%20said.%20But%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20will%20have%20to%20come%20back%20with%20a%20really%20strong%20collection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20business%20changes%20likely%20should%20happen.%20Brands%20that%20have%20resisted%20cyclicality%20tend%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20ultrarich%20and%20affluent%2C%20who%20are%20less%20affected%20by%20economic%20downturns.%20Analysts%20suggest%20the%20brand%20should%20continue%20to%20close%20outlets%20and%20offer%20fewer%20discounted%20goods%20to%20achieve%20the%20scarcity%20that%20makes%20uber-luxury%20brands%20so%20appealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20label%20could%20also%20stand%20not%20to%20repeat%20history%20%E2%80%94%20and%20diversify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20a%20much%20bigger%20brand%2C%20and%20they%20cannot%20just%20rely%20on%20one%20creative%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20Sokolova%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20that%20could%20mean%20embracing%20certain%20signatures%20that%20eschew%20trends%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fhow-to-buy-a-birkin-bag%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHerm%C3%A8s'%20Birkin%20bag%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20or%20Louis%20Vuitton's%20Neverfull.%20These%20looks%20hold%20their%20value%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0making%20them%20good%20investment%20pieces%20no%20matter%20the%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20De%20Sarno%20wasn't%20given%20much%20of%20a%20shot%20to%20do%20all%20this%20before%20the%20negative%20press%20started%20to%20hit%20the%20stands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20luxury%20industry%2C%20enthusiasm%20for%20dramatic%20headline%20news%20can%20often%20be%20overdone%2C'%20Chauvet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Pinault%20is%20quick%20to%20hammer%20home%2C%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20build%20a%20following%2C%20and%20Kering%20is%20ramping%20up%20its%20marketing%20for%20the%20label%20after%20recently%20hiring%20a%20Louis%20Vuitton%20veteran%20as%20deputy%20CEO.%20So%20far%2C%20there%20simply%20have%20not%20been%20enough%20De%20Sarno%20styles%20physically%20available%20to%20assess%20how%20the%20public%20is%20receiving%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrends%20also%20shift%20more%20quickly%20than%20ever%20in%20the%20age%20of%20social%20media%2C%20and%20De%20Sarno%20may%20create%20a%20design%20that%20breaks%20the%20internet%20in%20a%20collection%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20difficult%20when%20there%20is%20a%20transition%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20Euromonitor's%20Roberts%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20to%20say%20that%20De%20Sarno%20won't%20have%20the%20same%20effect%20%E2%80%94%20only%20time%20will%20tell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgucci-sales-profit-reputation-falling-luxury-kering-michele-china-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714729442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66315eba0dfb1341e900f51c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgucci-sales-profit-reputation-falling-luxury-kering-michele-china-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gucci's%20growth%20under%20Alessandro%20Michele%20was%20unsustainable.%20Its%20new%20designer%20now%20faces%20a%20struggle%20to%20reenergize%20the%20Kering%20luxury%20fashion%20brand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Madeline%20Berg)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgucci-sales-profit-reputation-falling-luxury-kering-michele-china-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ICC%20team%20rankings%3A%20India%20maintain%20supremacy%20in%20white-ball%20formats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714729364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109813523%2Cimgsize-63832.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Ficc-team-rankings-india-maintain-supremacy-in-white-ball-formats%