cost%20of%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20here%20is%20similar%20to%20a%20two-bedroom%20in%20Portland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20mall%2C%20many%20shops%2C%20and%20outdoor%20areas%20within%20a%20five-minute%20walk%20from%20me.%20I'm%20near%20bars%2C%20clubs%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20whatever%20I%20want%20to%20do.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20a%20car%20anymore%2C%20and%20as%20a%20pedestrian%2C%20it's%20very%20easy%20to%20get%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20plan%20to%20stay%20for%20a%20while%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20worst%20experience%20was%20my%20first%20time%20seeing%20a%20rat.%20You%20don't%20see%20rats%20on%20the%20street%20in%20Portland.%20I%20clearly%20haven't%20had%20any%20really%20bad%20experiences%20if%20that's%20the%20worst%20that's%20happened%20to%20me%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20downside%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbike-lanes-good-for-business-studies-better-streets-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiking%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20kind%20of%20nonexistent.%20There%20are%20bikes%20you%20can%20rent%20through%20an%20app%2C%20but%20there%20are%20no%20bike%20lanes%20and%20it%20feels%20almost%20dangerous%20to%20bike%20here%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20shocking%20to%20me%20coming%20from%20Portland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20like%20I%20can%20do%20anything%20I%20want%20here.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20moved%20halfway%20across%20the%20country%2C%20so%20I%20will%20probably%20stay%20here%20for%20a%20few%20years%20before%20moving%20to%20Europe%20when%20the%20time%20is%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20Chicago.%20I'm%20100%25%20sure%20I%20made%20the%20right%20decision%2C%20and%20I'm%20happier%20than%20I%20was%20in%20Oregon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-chicago-from-portland-big-city-life-affordable-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%2