%20before%20production%20started%20in%20Australia%20to%20work%20out%20how%20to%20do%20the%20beach%20cannon%20roll%2C%20and%20we%20spent%20months%20figuring%20out%20the%20perfect%20conditions%20and%20equipment%20to%20complete%20that%20stunt%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20planning%20another%20major%20stunt%20in%20the%20movie's%20climax.%20In%20this%20scene%2C%20Colt%20and%20Ryder%20drive%20off%20a%20ramp%2C%20launching%20their%20car%2080%20feet%20into%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20stunt%2C%20we%20brought%20in%20a%20trophy%20truck%20with%20suspension%20to%20handle%20a%20big%20jump%20and%20built%20a%2016-foot-high%20ramp%20on%20the%20ground.%20For%20the%20tests%2C%20we%20started%20at%20a%2075-foot%20jump%20distance%20and%20pushed%20back%20the%20end%20goal%20until%20we%20reached%20our%20200-foot%20jump%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20truck%20was%20set%20up%20to%20handle%20a%20200-foot%20jump%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20drive%20because%20the%20shock%20valve%20was%20very%20stiff%20and%20bouncy.%20This%20process%20took%20around%20100%20trial%20jumps%20before%20we%20were%20ready%20for%20the%20real%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20picture%20of%20the%20car%20jump.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633b48b10dfcda40965ef65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20side-by-side%20picture%20of%20the%20car%20jump.%3Cp%3EUniversal%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20jump%20was%20on%20a%2040-foot-high%20cliff%20edge%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20raise%20the%20ramp%20to%20the%20correct%20position.%20After%20scheduling%20delays%20due%20to%20rain%20and%20high%20winds%2C%20which%20could%20affect%20the%20jump%2C%20we%20finally%20filmed%20the%20stunt%20on%20a%20slightly%20breezy%20morning%20as%20the%20sun%20rose.%20The%20wind%20was%20starting%20to%20pick%20up%2C%20so%20we%20knew%20we%20might%20not%20get%20another%20chance%20at%20doing%20the%20jump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20crew's%20helicopter%20went%20to%20its%20position%2C%20the%20car%20was%20lined%20up%20to%20the%20ramp%20and%20then%20I%20was%20off.%20Driving%20up%20to%20the%20ramp%2C%20I%20had%20to%20reach%20the%20perfect%20speed.%20Too%20fast%20and%20my%20car%20could%20nose%20dive%20and%20flip%20when%20it%20landed.%20Too%20slow%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20make%20the%20landing%20pad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20hit%20the%20ramp%2C%20I%20couldn't%20see%20where%20I%20was%20landing.%20I%20was%20just%20a%20passenger%20to%20the%20elements%2C%20flying%20through%20the%20air%20and%20waiting%20to%20see%20where%20I%20landed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20enough%2C%20the%20tires%20hit%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20the%20same%20exhilarating%20feeling%20I%20had%20as%20a%20motorcycle%20racer%20before%20I%20became%20a%20stunt%20performer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20doing%20incredible%20stunts%20like%20these%20may%20make%20one%20feel%20invincible%2C%20I%20must%20always%20be%20focused%20and%20sharp%20to%20avoid%20mistakes.%20Getting%20complacent%20can%20be%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20completing%20two%20huge%20stunt%20scenes%20felt%20like%20a%20huge%20weight%20off%20my%20shoulders.%20Now%2C%20everyone%20can%20see%20the%20fruits%20of%20my%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-fall-guy-stunt-driver-guinness-world-record-car-roll-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714725002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633b031ec0c696569003006%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-fall-guy-stunt-driver-guinness-world-record-car-roll-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Logan%20Holladay%2C%20Ryan%20Gosling's%20stunt%20driver%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fall%20Guy%2C%26quot%3B%20told%