thi%20for%20fear%20of%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20I%20also%20want%20to%20tell%20him%2C%20Daro%20Mat%20(don't%20be%20afraid)%2C%20Bhaago%20Mat%20(don't%20run)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20sneered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20has%20often%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDaro%20Mat%26quot%3B%20while%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20using%20probe%20agencies%20to%20terrorise%20critics%20and%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20didn't%20spare%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20either%2C%20saying%20he%20had%20predicted%20that%20both%20mother%20and%20son%20would%20avoid%20contesting%20from%20their%20seats%20out%20of%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20said%2C%20their%20biggest%20leader%20will%20not%20dare%20to%20contest.%20She%20will%20run%20away%20out%20of%20fear.%20She%20ran%20to%20Rajasthan%20and%20from%20there%20entered%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20That%20is%20exactly%20what%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20said%20that%20shehzade%20(Rahul%20Gandhi)%20is%20afraid%20of%20losing%20in%20Wayanad%2C%20and%20the%20moment%20voting%20ends%2C%20he%20will%20start%20looking%20for%20a%20third%20seat.%20Now%20even%20from%20Amethi%2C%20despite%20all%20his%20loyalists%20saying%20it%2C%20he%20panicked%20so%20much%2C%20he%20ran%20from%20there%20and%20is%20now%20looking%20towards%20Raebareli.%20These%20people%20keep%20going%20around%20telling%20people%20Daro%20Mat.%20Today%20I%20will%20also%20tell%20them...%20ji%20bhar%20ke%20kehta%20hoon.%20Arey%20daro%20mat%2C%20bhaago%20mat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20BJP%20leaders%20seized%20on%20the%20Amethi-Raebareli%20decision%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20dead%20giveaway%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20knows%20he%20can't%20win%20Amethi%2C%20where%20Smriti%20Irani%20is%20contesting%20again%20after%20her%20shock%20win%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20while%20ago%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20used%20to%20say%20'daro%20mat%2C%20daro%20mat%2C%20daro%20mat'.%20Now%20his%20fear%20has%20taken%20him%20from%20Amethi%20to%20Wayanad%20and%20from%20Wayanad%20to%20Raebareli%20-%20the%20decision%20shows%20where%20all%20his%20fear%20of%20defeat%20is%20driving%20him.%20And%20the%20fear%20is%20also%20about%20whether%20he%20could%20lose%20both%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Union%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%2C%20who%20is%20the%20BJP's%20candidate%20from%20Hamirpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20failed%20to%20do%20right%20by%20his%20sister%20(Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra)%2C%20as%20on%20one%20hand%20Robert%20Vadra%20was%20asking%20for%20a%20ticket%20(to%20contest%20from%20Amethi)%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Congress%20workers%20wanted%20Priyanka%20Gandhi.%20Yet%20her%20name%20was%20not%20on%20the%20party's%20list%20-%20that%20shows%20something%20is%20going%20on%20within%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20they%20should%20tell%20the%20country%20what%20it%20is...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20BJP%20leader%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Brajesh%20Pathak%2C%20said%20the%20people%20of%20Raebareli%20would%20never%20accept%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20%26quot%3BBJP%20is%20going%20to%20win%20in%20Raebareli%20and%20Amethi%20by%20a%20huge%20margin.%20The%20people%20of%20Raebareli%20will%20never%20accept%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaebareli%20was%20held%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20became%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20from%20Rajasthan%20last%20month.%20As%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20moves%20to%20Raebareli%2C%20historically%20one%20of%20Congress's%20safest%20seats%2C%20his%20rival%20is%20the%20BJP's%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20who%20lost%20to%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20by%20over%201.67%20lakh%20votes%20in%20the%202019%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%20scored%20a%20stunning%20victory%20from%20Amethi%2C%20a%20constituency%20that%20had%20always%20been%20loyal%20to%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family.%20For%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20saving%20grace%20was%20his%20victory%20in%20the%20second%20seat%20he%20contested%20-%20Wayanad%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20named%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%20for%20Amethi.%20He%20dismissed%20the%20BJP's%20allegation%20that%20the%20Gandhis%20opted%20out%20of%20Amethi%20because%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bscared%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20is%20not%20someone%20who%20runs%20away%20from%20the%20ground.%20He%20is%20fighting%20for%20the%20whole%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20seats%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20fifth%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20on%20May%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20contesting%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20as%20part%20of%20its%20seat-sharing%20pact%20with%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20kept%20its%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%20announcement%20for%20the%20last%20minute%20as%20top%20leaders%20discussed%20the%20possibility%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20fighting%20from%20Amethi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20from%20Raebareli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20party%20requested%20Rahul%20to%20contest%20from%20Raebareli%20and%20he%20agreed.%20For%20us%2C%20Raebareli%2C%20Amethi%2C%20and%20Wayanad%20seats%20are%20all%20dear.%20Raebareli%20is%20the%20seat%20which%20was%20held%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20till%20recently%20it%20was%20held%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%20At%20the%20appropriate%20time%2C%20the%20party%20will%20decide%20which%20seat%20he%20will%20retain.%20The%20decision%20when%20taken%20will%20not%20affect%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Congress%20leader%20KC%20Venugopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWayanad%20voted%20on%20April%2026%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714723200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F6387g7j_pm-modi-rahul-gandhi-650-_650x400_03_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fused-to-say-daro-mat-bjp-pm-mo