.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fthe-split-special-barcelona-abi-morgan-1235989928%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fthe-split-special-barcelona-abi-morgan-1235989928%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fthe-split-special-barcelona-abi-morgan-1235989928%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Behind%20Parcel%20Bomb%20That%20Killed%20Gujarat%20Man%2C%20An%20Affair%20Gone%20Wrong%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20parcel%20that%20exploded%20and%20killed%20a%20man%20and%20his%20daughter%20in%20Gujarat's%20Vadali%20was%20sent%20to%20their%20house%20by%20a%20man%20who%20was%20allegedly%20having%20an%20affair%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon%20after%20the%20family%20opened%20the%20parcel%20and%20it%20exploded%20killing%2032-year-old%20Jeetubhai%20Heerabhai%20Vanjara%2C%20a%20labourer%2C%20on%20the%20spot%20while%20his%20daughter%20Bhumika%2C%2012%2C%20died%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20Jayantibhai%20Balusingh%20Vanjara%2C%2031%2C%20sent%20the%20parcel%20to%20Jeetubhai's%20house%20in%20an%20auto%20rickshaw%2C%20making%20it%20appear%20like%20a%20tape%20recorder.%20When%20the%20Jeetubhai%20tried%20to%20plug%20it%20in%2C%20the%20box%20exploded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20police%20officer%20Vijay%20Patel%20said%20that%20during%20the%20initial%20investigation%2C%20the%20auto-rickshaw%20driver%20who%20delivered%20the%20package%20to%20the%20house%20was%20identified%20based%20on%20the%20CCTV%20footage.%20Based%20on%20the%20auto%20driver's%20statement%2C%20police%20formed%20teams%20to%20locate%20the%20accused%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20hours%20after%20the%20blast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayantibhai%20had%20sent%20the%20parcel%20to%20Jeetubhai's%20house%20to%20kill%20him%20as%20he%20did%20not%20approve%20of%20his%20former%20girlfriend's%20marriage%20to%20Jeetubhai%2C%20he%20said.%20Jayantibhai%20travelled%20to%20Rajasthan%20to%20get%20the%20materials%20to%20make%20the%20improvised%20bomb.%20He%20used%20gelatin%20sticks%20and%20a%20detonator%20which%20was%20set%20off%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Btape%20recorder%26quot%3B%20was%20plugged%20in%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJeetubhai's%20other%20two%20daughters%2C%20aged%209%20and%2010%2C%20were%20also%20injured%20in%20the%20explosion%20and%20are%20being%20treated.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20on%20ventilator%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sisters%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20Ahmedabad%20for%20further%20treatment.%20Both%20have%20sustained%20severe%20injuries%20in%20their%20eyes%20and%20chest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20Jeetubhai's%20wife%20was%20out%20of%20the%20house%20when%20the%20explosion%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20investigation%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Mahendra%20Prasad)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714722660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fuhes788_gujarat-blast_625x300_02_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbehind-parcel-bomb-that-killed-gujarat-man-an-affair-gone-wrong-5578786%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20parcel%20that%20exploded%20and%20killed%20a%20man%20and%20his%20daughter%20in%20Gujarat's%20Vadali%20was%20sent%20to%20their%20house%20by%20a%20man%20who%20was%20allegedly%20having%20an%20affair%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbehind-parcel-bomb-that-killed-gujarat-man-an-affair-gone-wrong-5578786%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbehind-parcel-bomb-that-killed-gujarat-man-an-affair-gone-wrong-5578786%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbehind-parcel-bomb-that-killed-gujarat-man-an-affair-gone-wrong-5578786%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'If%20Someone%20Is%20Named%20Rahul%20Gandhi...'%3A%20Court's%20'No'%20To%20Ban%20Poll%20Namesakes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERejecting%20a%20request%20for%20a%20ban%20on%20namesake%20candidates%20in%20elections%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20it%20cannot%20stop%20people%20from%20contesting%20polls%20if%20they%20are%20named%20after%20political%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPetitioner%20Sabu%20Stephen%20had%20moved%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%2C%20arguing%20that%20namesake%20candidates%20are%20propped%20up%20in%20high-profile%20seats%20to%20mislead%20voters.%20The%20petitioner%20stressed%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20such%20candidates%20has%20often%20led%20to%20heavyweight%20candidates%20losing%20by%20a%20slim%20margin.%20The%20petition%20sought%20a%20direction%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20take%20urgent%20steps%20to%20stop%20this%20trend%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERefusing%20to%20hear%20the%20matter%2C%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20parents%20have%20given%20similar%20names%20to%20candidates%2C%20how%20can%20they%20be%20prevented%20from%20contesting%20polls%3F%20Like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav.%26quot%3B%20The%20court%20allowed%20the%20petitioner%20to%20withdraw%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENamesake%20candidates%20are%20part%20of%20an%20age-old%20election%20trick%20in%20which%20candidates%20with%20names%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20a%20heavyweight%20are%20propped%20up%20by%20rival%20parties.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20confuse%20voters%20and%20get%20them%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20namesakes%2C%20effectively%20harming%20the%20heavyweight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20in%20question%20is%20the%20Ramanathapuram%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Former%20Chief%20Minister%20O%20Panneerselvam%2C%20also%20known%20as%20OPS%2C%20is%20contesting%20as%20an%20Independent%20this%20time.%20Besides%20the%20former%20AIADMK%20leader%2C%20there%20are%20four%20other%20Panneerselvams%20in%20the%20list%20of%20candidates.%20They%20are%20Ochappan%20Panneerselvam%2C%20Oyya%20Thevar%20Panneerselvam%2C%20Ocha%20Thevar%20Panneerselvam%2C%20and%20Oyyaram%20Panneerselvam%20--%20all%20of%20them%20Independent%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experiment%20is%20being%20attempted%20in%20other%20states%20too.%20In%20Maharashtra's%20Raigad%20seat%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20has%20fielded%20Anant%20Geete.%20He%20is%20up%20against%20NCP's%20Sunil%20Tatkare.%20But%20two%20more%20Anant%20Geetes%20have%20signed%20for%20the%20poll%20fight%20as%20Independents.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714722600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-someone-is-named-rahul-gandhi-supreme-courts-no-to-ban-poll-namesakes-5578769%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rejecting%20a%20request%20for%20a%20ban%20on%20namesake%20candidates%20in%20elections%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20it%20cannot%20stop%20people%20from%20contesting%20polls%20if%20they%20are%20named%20after%20political%20leaders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-someone-is-named-rahul-gandhi-supreme-courts-no-to-ban-poll-namesakes-5578769%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-someone-is-named-rahul-gandhi-supreme-courts-no-to-ban-poll-namesakes-5578769%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-someone-is-named-rahul-gandhi-supreme-courts-no-to-ban-poll-namesakes-5578769%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Smriti%20Irani's%20%26quot%3BProxy%26quot%3B%20Jibe%20After%20Congress%20Fields%20A%20Non-Gandhi%20From%20Amethi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20today%20taunted%20the%20Gandhis%20for%20fielding%20a%20%26quot%3Bproxy%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Amethi%20constituency%20and%20not%20one%20of%20the%20family%20members%20to%20reclaim%20their%20lost%20fortress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20ended%20the%20Amethi%20suspense%20this%20morning%2C%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20filing%20nominations%2C%20and%20fielded%20KL%20Sharma%2C%20a%20loyalist%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%2C%20for%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gandhis%20would%20have%20fought%20themselves%20and%20not%20fielded%20a%20proxy%20if%20they%20felt%20they%20could%20win%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20leave%20any%20stone%20unturned%20in%20welcoming%20our%20guests.%20Congress's%20decision%20to%20not%20field%20anyone%20from%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20in%20Amethi%20signifies%20that%20it%20has%20accepted%20defeat%20even%20before%20voting%20takes%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20actor-turned-politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20decision%20to%20field%20a%20non-Gandhi%20candidate%20from%20Amethi%20came%20amid%20speculations%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20try%20to%20win%20back%20the%20seat%20that%20he%20had%20won%20thrice%20in%20the%20past.%20But%20Mr%20Gandhi%20was%20named%20for%20Raebareli%2C%20which%20was%20vacated%20by%20his%20mother%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20is%20a%20second%20seat%20for%20him%20after%20Wayanad%20(Kerala).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20won%20Amethi%20in%202004%2C%202009%2C%20and%202014%2C%20but%20a%20shock%20defeat%20to%20Ms%20Irani%20in%202019%20reduced%20the%20Congress's%20UP%20footprint.%20He%20had%20contested%20Wayanad%20in%202019%20as%20a%20second%20seat%20and%20won%20it%20to%20retain%20his%20MP%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20reached%20Raebareli%20on%20a%20chartered%20flight%20this%20morning%20after%20his%20party%20announced%20him%20as%20a%20candidate.%20He%20will%20be%20filing%20his%20nomination%20later%20in%20the%20day.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20his%20sister%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20and%20his%20top%20aides%20are%20also%20accompanying%20him%20for%20filing%20his%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714722600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F13tlidqo_smriti-irani_625x300_03_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsmriti-iranis-proxy-jibe-after-congress-fields-a-non-gandhi-from-amethi-5578723%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20today%20taunted%20the%20Gandhis%20for%20fielding%20a%20%26quot%3Bproxy%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Amethi%20constituency%20and%20not%20one%20of%20their%20family%20members%20to%20reclaim%20their%20lost%20fortress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsmriti-iranis-proxy-jibe-after-congress-fields-a-non-gandhi-from-amethi-5578723%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsmriti-iranis-proxy-jibe-after-congress-fields-a-non-gandhi-from-amethi-5578723%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsmriti-iranis-proxy-jibe-after-congress-fields-a-non-gandhi-from-amethi-5578723%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sonakshi%20Sinha%20on%20Salman%20Khan's%20work%20ethics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714722471000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109809678%2Cimgsize-31666.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fheeramandi-actress-sonakshi-sinha-on-salman-khans-work-ethics-he-has-mastered-the-art-of-understanding-his-audience%2Farticleshow%2F109809602.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%2