was%20named%20as%20the%20vice-captain%20of%20India's%2015-member%20squad%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20despite%20the%20clouds%20of%20criticism%20looming%20over%20him.%20Ojha%20showed%20his%20faith%20in%20Hardik's%20leadership%20skills%20and%20his%20all-round%20abilities%2C%20emphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20mentally%20prepared%20to%20take%20charge%20if%20fate%20demanded.%20%26quot%3BI%20expect%20him%20to%20play%20like%20a%20leader%20because%20he%20is%20next%20in%20command.%20If%20something%20happens%20to%20Rohit%2C%20we%20don't%20want%20that%2C%20if%20anything%20happens%2C%20he%20(Hardik)%20will%20be%20leading%20the%20side%2C%20so%20he%20has%20to%20be%20prepared%2C%20he%20has%20to%20take%20that%20responsibility%20when%20he%20is%20batting%2C%26quot%3B%20Ojha%20said%20to%20Jio%20Cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20Hardik%20played%20for%20India%20was%20in%20the%20October%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20Bangladesh.%20Before%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%202024%2C%20he%20made%20a%20full%20recovery%20from%20an%20ankle%20ailment%20and%20was%20named%20captain%20of%20the%20five-time%20champions%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20replacing%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20invited%20a%20lot%20of%20social%20media%20criticism%2C%20which%20somewhere%20damaged%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20all-rounder.%20He%20has%20managed%20to%20score%20197%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%20150.38%20in%2010%20games%20in%20the%202024%20season%20so%20far.%20Only%20six%20wickets%20have%20been%20claimed%20by%20the%20all-rounder%20at%20an%20economy%20rate%20of%2011.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOjha%2C%20acknowledging%20Hardik's%20significance%20in%20the%20Indian%20setup%2C%20lauded%20his%20ability%20to%20provide%20balance%20to%20the%20team.%20Despite%20the%20IPL%20ordeal%2C%20Hardik's%20place%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad%20was%20never%20in%20doubt.%20His%20versatility%20as%20an%20all-rounder%20offered%20India%20the%20flexibility%20they%20needed%2C%20a%20fact%20not%20lost%20on%20selectors%20or%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20he%20is%20someone%20who%20will%20create%20that%20balance%20for%20the%20side.%20Every%20time%20we%20talk%20about%20Indian%20team%20selection%2C%20Hardik's%20name%20always%20comes%20in.%20He%20creates%20that%20balance%2C%20he%20will%20give%20you%20that%20cushion.%20That%20you%20can%20have%20an%20extra%20batter%20or%20a%20bowler%2C%20wherever%20he%20is%20needed.%20That's%20what%20we%20want%20him%20to%20do%2C%20to%20be%20mentally%20ready%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20just%20forget%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20that%20is%20more%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Ojha%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Mumbai%20Indians%20languishing%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20points%20table%20with%20just%20three%20wins%20in%20ten%20games%2C%20Hardik%20faced%20relentless%20scrutiny%20and%20his%20captaincy%20came%20under%20fire.%20He%20was%20not%20only%20booed%20by%20the%20crowds%20across%20venues%20but%20was%20also%20criticised%20by%20the%20experts%20for%20his%20captaincy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714721880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Ft16ksj5g_rohit-sharma-afp_625x300_20_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fif-something-happens-to-rohit-sharma-ex-stars-huge-massive-on-india-captaincy-5573308%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20is%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20across%20formats.%20He%20will%20be%20leading%20the%20side%20in%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%20as%20well.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20violence%3A%20