so%20experimental%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Patrick%20Frater%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fudine-festival-prizes-takano-tofu-1235991028%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fudine-festival-prizes-takano-tofu-1235991028%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fudine-festival-prizes-takano-tofu-1235991028%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raebareli%20Is%20Congress's%20Safe%20Seat%2C%20Except%20It%20Handed%20Defeat%20To%20A%20PM%20Once%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20much-awaited%20announcement%20of%20its%20candidates%20for%20Rae%20Bareli%20and%20Amethi%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20put%20the%20spotlight%20back%20on%20these%20two%20bastions%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family.%20The%20twin%20strongholds%20weathered%20many%20a%20political%20storm%2C%20including%20the%20wave%20in%20support%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202014%2C%20and%20remained%20with%20the%20Congress.%20In%202019%2C%20Amethi%20fell%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20Rae%20Bareli%20held%20fort.%20With%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20showing%20its%20cards%20for%20these%20seats%2C%20the%20game%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20history%20of%20these%202%20Congress%20bastions%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERae%20Bareli%3A%20Where%20A%20Sitting%20PM%20Lost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20Congress's%20safest%20seats%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country%20is%20Rae%20Bareli.%20Out%20of%20the%2020%20elections%20this%20seat%20has%20witnessed%20so%20far%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20won%2017.%20The%20Rae%20Bareli%20seat%20is%20also%20seeped%20in%20historical%20significance%20and%20has%20the%20distinction%20of%20being%20the%20only%20parliamentary%20constituency%20where%20a%20sitting%20Prime%20Minister%20suffered%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20represented%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20husband%20and%20freedom%20fighter%20Feroze%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20seat%20elected%20Indira%20Gandhi%20thrice.%20In%20June%201975%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20declared%20Mrs%20Gandhi's%201971%20victory%20from%20Rae%20Bareli%20void%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20electoral%20malpractice.%20The%20court%20banned%20her%20from%20running%20for%20any%20office%20for%20six%20years%2C%20setting%20in%20motion%20a%20chain%20of%20events%20that%20would%20culminate%20in%20the%20Emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201977%20elections%20after%20the%20Emergency%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20suffered%20a%20crushing%20defeat%20in%20the%20Congress%20stronghold%20--%20the%20only%20sitting%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20lose%20an%20election.%20And%20the%20one%20who%20defeated%20her%20was%20Raj%20Narain%2C%20who%20contested%20on%20a%20Janata%20Party%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%20made%20a%20comeback%20in%20the%201980%20election.%20In%20the%20years%20that%20followed%2C%20Arun%20Nehru%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family%2C%20was%20elected%20twice%20from%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20then%20suffered%20setbacks%20in%201996%20and%201998%20elections%2C%20when%20the%20BJP's%20Ashok%20Singh%20won%20from%20Rae%20Bareli.%20On%20both%20occasions%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20relegated%20to%20the%20third%20spot.%20The%20Congress%20managed%20to%20win%20Rae%20Bareli%20back%20in%201999%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20then%20held%20it%20for%20two%20decades%20--%202004%20to%202024%20--%20before%20vacating%20it%20to%20join%20Rajya%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20emotional%20letter%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Rae%20Bareli%20before%20she%20moved%20to%20the%20Upper%20House%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20losing%20my%20mother-in-law%20and%20my%20life%20partner%20forever%2C%20I%20came%20to%20you%20and%20you%20spread%20your%20arms%20for%20me.%20In%20the%20last%20two%20elections%2C%20you%20stood%20by%20me%20like%20a%20rock%20even%20in%20difficult%20circumstances%2C%20I%20can%20never%20forget%20this.%26quot%3B%20She%20had%20also%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20constituency%20will%20stand%20by%20her%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20gears%20up%20to%20contest%20from%20this%20prestige%20seat%2C%20he%20is%20up%20against%20the%20BJP's%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmethi%3A%20The%20Lost%20Bastion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20Amethi%20has%20been%20a%20Gandhi%20family%20stronghold%20for%20years%20and%20has%20been%20represented%20by%20as%20many%20as%20four%20Gandhis%20--%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20Created%20in%201967%2C%20Amethi%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20was%20first%20represented%20by%20Congress's%20Vijdya%20Dhar%20Bajpai.%20Sanjay%20Gandhi's%20first%20Lok%20Sabha%20outing%20from%20here%20ended%20in%20a%20defeat%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20routed%20in%20the%20first%20polls%20after%20Emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Gandhi%20won%20the%20seat%20in%201980%20elections%2C%20but%20it%20was%20vacated%20due%20to%20his%20death%20in%20an%20air%20crash%20soon%20after.%20In%20the%20four%20elections%20that%20followed%2C%20Amethi%20elected%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%20Tragedy%20struck%20in%201991%20when%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20assassinated%20days%20after%20polling%20in%20Amethi.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20later%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20won%20the%20election.%20Amethi%20elected%20his%20wife%20and%20top%20Congress%20leader%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20in%201999.%20She%20vacated%20the%20seat%20for%20her%20son%20Rahul%20in%202004%20who%20won%20it%20thrice%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20election%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Smriti%20Irani%20scored%20a%20surprise%20win%20over%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20defeating%20him%20by%20over%2050%2C000%20votes.%20This%20time%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20decided%20to%20contest%20from%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20leading%20the%20BJP%20to%20call%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Brunaway%20soldier%26quot%3B.%20To%20take%20on%20Ms%20Irani%20from%20the%20prestige%20seat%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20chosen%20KL%20Sharma%2C%20a%20long-term%20loyalist%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20who%20has%20earlier%20served%20as%20the%20MP's%20representative%20in%20Rae%20Bareli%20and%20has%20also%20worked%20extensively%20in%20Amethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20has%20said%20Mr%20Sharma's%20%26quot%3Bdedication%20and%20sense%20of%20duty%20will%20surely%20bring%20him%20success%20in%20this%20election%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Dynasty%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20Congress's%20last-minute%20announcement%20of%20its%20candidates%20in%20Rae%20Bareli%20and%20Amethi%2C%20speculation%20was%20rife%20that%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20may%20be%20contesting%20from%20one%20of%20the%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%20in%20the%20party%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20requested%20her%20to%20contest%20from%20Amethi%20or%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20but%20she%20refused.%20Behind%20her%20reluctance%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20victory%20for%20her%20and%20her%20brother%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20would%20put%20three%20members%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20in%20Parliament%20--%20mother%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20is%20now%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20This%20would%20reinforce%20the%20BJP's%20charge%20of%20dynastic%20politics%2C%20she%20reasoned%2C%20according%20to%20sources%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20changed%20political%20atmosphere%20and%20the%20BJP's%20dynasty%20attack%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20holding%20on%20to%20a%20family%20stronghold%20may%20have%20gone%20against%20the%20Congress.%20Another%20line%20of%20argument%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20has%20strong%20connections%20to%20these%20two%20seats%20and%20their%20star%20power%20does%20add%20to%20the%20Congress's%20advantage.%20So%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20Gandhi%20among%20the%20candidates%20in%20Amethi%20may%20just%20give%20sitting%20MP%20Smriti%20Irani%20an%20edge%20in%20the%20prestige%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714720740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fhcktrb9_priyanka-rahul-sonia_625x300_03_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famethi-rae-bareli-elections-2024-rae-bareli-is-congresss-safe-seat-except-it-handed-defeat-to-a-pm-once-5578109%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress's%20much-awaited%20announcement%20of%20its%20candidates%20for%20Rae%20Bareli%20and%20Amethi%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20put%20the%20spotlight%20back%20on%20these%20two%20bastions%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famethi-rae-bareli-elections-2024-rae-bareli-is-congresss-safe-seat-except-it-handed-defeat-to-a-pm-once-5578109%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famethi-rae-bareli-elections-2024-rae-bareli-is-congresss-safe-seat-except-it-handed-defeat-to-a-pm-once-5578109%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famethi-rae-bareli-elections-2024-rae-bareli-is-congresss-safe-seat-except-it-handed-defeat-to-a-pm-once-5578109%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20iPhone%20sales%20fall%20in%20nearly%20all%20countries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714720642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fc105%2Flive%2Fa668ead0-091d-11ef-83ed-6d2edc1b7cdb.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc99zxzjqw2ko%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20tech%20giant%20says%20demand%20for%20its%20smartphones%20fell%20more%20than%2010%25%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%20the%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagemen