News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F61chqhm_prajwal-revanna_650x400_29_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20pressure%20from%20all%20sides%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmp-prajwal-revanna-suspended-from-jds-over-sex-scandal-row-5555205%5C%22%3EJanata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20(JD-S)%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20Hassan%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-driver-who-leaked-sex-tapes-goes-missing-amid-probe-5571371%5C%22%3EPrajwal%20Revanna%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20the%20party%20on%20April%2030%20over%20an%20alleged%20sex%20scandal.%20This%20decision%20was%20welcomed%20by%20its%20ally%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-sex-scandal-prajwal-revannas-ex-driver-bjp-leader-accuse-each-other-of-leaking-videos-5556892%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20political%20storm%20surrounding%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20grandson%20of%20former%20Indian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-cops-reject-prajwal-revannas-request-for-time-to-join-sex-harassment-probe-5570589%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20H.D.%20Deve%20Gowda%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20unsurprising%20given%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20for%2014%20of%20Karnataka's%2028%20seats%2C%20including%20Hassan%2C%20where%20Prajwal%20has%20again%20contested%2C%20took%20place%20on%20April%2026.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20remaining%2014%20seats%20scheduled%20for%20polling%20in%20the%20third%20phase%20on%20May%207%2C%20there%20was%20mounting%20pressure%20from%20the%20BJP%20to%20take%20action%20against%20Prajwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20is%20yet%20another%20example%20of%20the%20moral%20bankruptcy%20of%20politicians%20and%20the%20abuse%20of%20their%20positions.%20The%20disgrace%20and%20horror%20are%20heightened%20when%20it%20involves%20democratically%20elected%20representatives%20like%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%2C%20whom%20people%20approach%20with%20their%20grievances%20expecting%20resolution.%20The%20selective%20outrage%20of%20political%20parties%20and%20their%20leadership%20against%20crimes%20against%20women%20is%20equally%20abhorrent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECriminal%20Lawmakers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20report%20released%20in%20August%202023%2C%20134%20sitting%20members%20of%20parliament%20(MPs)%20and%20members%20of%20legislative%20assemblies%20(MLAs)%20have%20cases%20related%20to%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20including%2021%20MPs%20and%20113%20MLAs.%20This%20data%20is%20based%20on%20ADR's%20analysis%20of%20762%20sitting%20MPs%20and%204%2C001%20sitting%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20political%20parties%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%2044%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20against%20whom%20cases%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20have%20been%20registered%2C%20including%20seven%20MPs.%20The%20Congress%20had%2025%2C%20followed%20by%20AAP%20with%2013%20sitting%20MPs%20or%20MLAs%20who%20have%20declared%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20involving%20Prajwal's%20sexual%20crimes%20surpasses%20all%20previous%20instances%20of%20perversion.%20Thousands%20of%20girls%20and%20women%20from%20various%20backgrounds%20(government%20officials%2C%20TV%20anchors%2C%20models%2C%20minors%2C%20maids)%20have%20allegedly%20been%20sexually%20exploited%2C%20with%20graphic%20details%20of%20the%20acts%20recorded%20on%20video.%20The%20perpetrator%20has%20reportedly%20recorded%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20victims%20while%20himself%20remaining%20hidden%20in%20most%20cases.%20An%20FIR%20has%20been%20lodged%20by%20one%20of%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoliticisation%20of%20Victims'%20Plight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circumstances%20under%20which%20these%20women%20were%20forced%20into%20such%20situations%20remain%20unknown.%20However%2C%20the%20trauma%20and%20agony%20experienced%20by%20these%20female%20victims%20are%20unimaginable.%20Reports%20from%20the%20ground%20suggest%20that%20women%20caught%20in%20the%20act%20are%20facing%20abandonment%20by%20their%20families%2C%20with%20husbands%2C%20children%2C%20and%20acquaintances%20shaming%20and%20disowning%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fprajwal-revanna-sex-scandal-and-lawmakers-patchy-record-in-crimes-against-women-5572732%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20Women%20And%20Politics%20-%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20Case%20Raises%20Uneasy%20Questions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20government%20has%20established%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20to%20probe%20the%20crime%2C%20but%20questions%20remain%20about%20its%20adequacy.%20There%20are%20allegations%20that%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20not%20only%20knew%20about%20the%20videos%20but%20also%20possessed%20copies%20of%20them%20and%20was%20waiting%20for%20an%20opportune%20moment%20-%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20-%20to%20release%20and%20capitalise%20on%20them.%20Sources%20claim%20that%20Karthik%2C%20a%20driver%20for%20the%20Revanna%20family%20who%20had%20personal%20issues%20with%20them%2C%20provided%20a%20pen%20drive%20containing%20the%20alleged%20acts%20to%20Karnataka's%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20D.K.%20Shivakumar.%20Subsequently%2C%20it%20is%20alleged%20that%20multiple%20copies%20were%20made%20and%20distributed%20by%20ordinary%20Congress%20workers%20in%20many%20households%20in%20Hassan%20just%20days%20before%20the%20polling%20on%20April%2026.%20Of%20course%2C%20Shivakumar%20has%20refuted%20these%20claims%2C%20as%20has%20the%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20becomes%20murkier.%20In%20June%202023%2C%20Prajwal%20managed%20to%20secure%20a%20gag%20order%20against%20media%20outlets%20from%20a%20Bengaluru%20civil%20court%20regarding%20the%20same%20sexual%20assault%20videos%2C%20dismissing%20them%20as%20'fake'%20and%20'morphed'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20extremely%20influential%20family%20and%20it%20will%20be%20a%20herculean%20task%20for%20the%20SIT%20to%20investigate.%20The%20political%20parties%20have%20no%20interest%20in%20investigating%20the%20case.%20They%20have%20already%20started%20their%20mudslinging.%20The%20victims'%20lives%20are%20under%20threat.%20Stories%20are%20already%20floating%20around%20about%20sexual%20acts%20being%20consensual%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Vimala%20K.S.%2C%20Vice-President%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20unit%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Democratic%20Women's%20Association.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaximum%20Mileage%20for%20Electoral%20Gains%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20were%20the%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20videos%20a%20ploy%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprajwal-revanna-cops-reject-prajwal-revannas-request-for-time-to-join-sex-harassment-probe-5570589%5C%22%3Ethe%20Congress%20party%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20gain%20maximum%20electoral%20advantage%20from%20the%20scandal%20in%20the%20remaining%20phases%20of%20general%20elections%2C%20both%20within%20the%20state%20and%20nationwide%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20if%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20case%20for%20months%2C%20why%20did%20it%20fail%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%20and%20launch%20investigations%20against%20him%3F%20The%20motives%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20are%20suspect%20because%20of%20its%20failure%20to%20act%20promptly.%20There%20was%20such%20a%20rush%20to%20gain%20political%20advantage%20that%20nobody%20bothered%20to%20blur%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20were%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-protect-him-says-hd-kumaraswamy-uncle-of-karnataka-mp-prajwal-revanna-in-video-scandal-5555096%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%26quot%3BWon't%20Protect%20Him%26quot%3B%3A%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20Uncle%20Of%20Karnataka%20MP%20In%20Video%20Scandal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SIT%20should%20investigate%20as%20to%20who%20leaked%20the%20video%2C%20because%20that%2C%20too%2C%20is%20a%20crime.%20People%20are%20cynical%20about%20justice%20being%20done%20because%20there%20is%20already%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20women%20from%20the%20Deve%20Gowda%20family.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20FIR%20hasn't%20been%20registered%20under%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%20which%20may%20weaken%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Vinay%20Sreenivasa%2C%20an%20advocate%20based%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasises%20the%20need%20for%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20to%20create%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20the%20survivors%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20SIT%20should%20include%20a%20retired%20judge%2C%20women%20activists%2C%20and%20officials%20from%20the%20home%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20and%20its%20national%20leaders%2C%20including%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%2C%20should%20be%20directing%20pertinent%20questions%20to%20the%20Congress%20state%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20instead%20of%20attempting%20to%20gain%20electoral%20mileage%20through%20public%20rallies%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20JD(S)'s%20ally%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20must%20come%20clean%20on%20whether%20the%20leadership%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20perverted%20videos%20while%20allowing%20Revanna%20to%20seek%20re-election%20from%20the%20Hassan%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20well-known%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20incidents%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20involving%20high-profile%20politicians%20across%20party%20lines%2C%20political%20parties%20often%20refuse%20to%20acknowledge%2C%20let%20alone%20address%2C%20the%20issue.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIf%20it's%20the%20same%20this%20time%20too%2C%20it%20would%20be%20tragic%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714719960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F61chqhm_prajwal-revanna_650x400_29_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fprajwal-revanna-sex-scandal-is-shameful-so-is-its-politicisation-5578289%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Prajwal%20case%20is%20yet%20another%20example%20of%20the%20moral%20bankruptcy%20of%20politicians%20and%20the%20abuse%20of%20their%20positions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fprajwal-revanna-sex-scandal-is-shameful-so-is-its-politicisation-5578289%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saad%20Bilgrami's%20emotional%20connect%20to%20Panchayat%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714719875000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109808089%2Cimgsize-61166.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fsaad-bilgrami-opens-up-about-his-emotional-connection-to-panchayat-3%2Farticleshow%2F109807985.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109807985.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E'Panchayat%203'%20is%20the%20eagerly%20anticipated%20OTT%20series%2C%20gaining%20traction%20from%20its%20predecessors'%20acclaim.%20Recently%2C%20Saad%20Bilgrami%2C%20known%20for%20his%20roles%20in%20'Gullak'%20and%20'Khuda%20Haafiz'%2C%20shared%20insights%20about%20his%20role%20in%20the%20series.%20Directed%20by%20Deepak%20Kumar%20Mishra%20and%20written%20by%20