tostory%2F109807735.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Heard%20Him%20Whine%20But%20Setbacks%20Affected%20Him%26quot%3B%3A%20KKR%20Coach%20On%20Shreyas%20Iyer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20his%20side's%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20match%20against%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%2C%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20assistant%20coach%20Abhishek%20Nayar%20hailed%20skipper%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20for%20his%20mental%20strength%20and%20positive%20approach%20to%20life%20despite%20some%20ups%20and%20downs%20during%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20which%20include%20an%20all-time%20great%20campaign%20in%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%2C%20back%20injuries%2C%20losing%20his%20Team%20India%20central%20contract%20and%20getting%20his%20commitment%20to%20red-ball%20cricket%20doubted%20on.%20MI%20and%20KKR%20will%20be%20locking%20horns%20in%20a%20high-octane%20clash%20at%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20Friday.%20KKR%20is%20at%20the%20second%20spot%20in%20the%20points%20table%2C%20with%20six%20wins%20and%20three%20losses%2C%20giving%20them%2012%20points.%20They%20won%20their%20previous%20clash%20against%20Delhi%20Capitals.%20MI%20is%20in%20the%20ninth%20spot%20with%20three%20wins%20and%20seven%20losses%2C%20giving%20them%20just%20six%20points.%20They%20lost%20their%20previous%20game%20to%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20mixed%20last%20few%20months%20for%20Iyer.%20After%20missing%20the%20IPL%202023%20due%20to%20back%20surgery%20with%20the%20World%20Cup%20on%20his%20mind%2C%20the%20right-handed%20batter%20made%20his%20return%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20following%20which%20he%20continued%20to%20battle%20fitness%20issues.%20He%20did%20make%20a%20return%20during%20the%20next%20series%20against%20Australia%2C%20scoring%20a%20century%20in%20one%20of%20the%20ODIs%20and%20solidifying%20for%20himself%20a%20middle-order%20spot%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20where%20he%20broke%20numerous%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20tough%20start%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%20Iyer%20achieved%20his%20peak%20form%20near%20the%20tournament%20end%2C%20with%20half-centuries%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20South%20Africa%20and%20two%20successive%20centuries%20against%20the%20Netherlands%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20coming%20in%20the%20semifinals%20against%20India's%20arch-nemesis%20that%20had%20denied%20Team%20India%20a%20shot%20at%20ICC%20title%20glory%20since%20so%20long.%20His%20hundred%2C%20that%20came%20in%2067%20balls%2C%20was%20the%20fastest-ever%20in%20a%20knockout%20WC%20game.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20dismissed%20for%20just%20four%20runs%20in%20the%20final%20which%20India%20lost%20to%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIyer%20ended%20the%20tournament%20with%20530%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2066.25%20with%20two%20centuries%20and%20three%20fifties%2C%20scoring%20the%20most%20runs%20by%20a%20middle-order%20batter%20in%20the%20tournament's%20history%20and%20becoming%20the%20first-ever%20middle-order%20batter%20in%20WC%20to%20touch%20the%20500-run%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%20after%20it%2C%20Iyer%20had%20a%20disappointing%20Test%20outing%20in%20South%20Africa.%20He%20warmed%20up%20for%20the%20next%20Test%20challenge%20against%20England%20at%20home%20from%20January%20to%20March%20by%20playing%20a%20Ranji%20Trophy%20match%2C%20but%20he%20was%20dropped%20from%20the%20remaining%20three%20Tests%20after%20poor%20scores%20in%20first%20two%20Tests.%20He%20then%20missed%20the%20Ranji%20quarters%20due%20to%20back%20spasm%2C%20despite%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India's%20(BCCI)'s%20directive%20to%20not%20skip%20it.%20But%20he%20returned%20for%20the%20semifinal%20and%20scored%2095%20runs%20in%20the%20final%2C%20but%20missed%20a%20lot%20of%20game%20time%20during%20the%20title%20clash%20due%20to%20back%20pain.%20However%2C%20despite%20playing%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20Mumbai's%2042nd%20triumph%2C%20Iyer's%20return%20to%20domestic%20red-ball%20cricket%20seemed%20a%20little%20too%20late%20as%20his%20name%20was%20dropped%20from%20BCCI's%20Central%20Contract%20list%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20Iyer%20linked%20up%20with%20KKR%20and%20has%20featured%20in%20all%20games%20so%20far%2C%20scoring%20251%20runs%20in%20nine%20games%20at%20an%20average%20of%2041.83%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20137.15%2C%20with%20a%20half-century.%20Though%20he%20is%20not%20at%20his%20most%20fluent%2C%20he%20has%20still%20managed%20to%20score%20runs%20after%20momentum%20was%20set%20by%20top-order%20batters%20Phil%20Salt%20and%20Sunil%20Narine.%20Despite%20his%20efforts%2C%20he%20missed%20his%20chance%20to%20get%20selected%20for%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20this%20year%20in%20West%20Indies%2FUSA%20from%20June%201%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENayar%2C%20who%20has%20known%20Iyer%20since%20his%20early%20days%20of%20playing%20domestic%20cricket%20for%20Mumbai%2C%20said%20that%20Iyer%20is%20one%20of%20the%20strongest%20people%20he%20has%20met%20and%20has%20dealt%20with%20all%20his%20setbacks%20with%20a%20positive%20attitude.%20Despite%20all%20the%20setbacks%2C%20Iyer%20is%20great%20on%20field%2C%20putting%20in%20long%20hours%20in%20nets%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20one%20of%20the%20strongest%20people%2C%20mentally%2C%20I%20have%20ever%20known%2C%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20he%20has%20accepted%20certain%20things%20that%20have%20happened%20with%20him.%20I%20would%20have%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20cribbing%20and%20talking%20about%20it%2C%20but%20I%20have%20not%20heard%20him%20whine%20about%20it%20or%20complain%20about%20it%20at%20all.%20The%20way%20he%20has%20approached%20life%20is%20in%20a%20positive%20manner%20-%20what%20is%20in%20front%20of%20you%2C%20you%20try%20and%20accept%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nayar%20as%20quoted%20by%20ESPNCricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertain%20things%20are%20not%20under%20his%20control%20but%20his%20fitness%20is%20in%20his%20control%2C%20and%20he%20is%20feeling%20a%20lot%20better%20now.%20He%20is%20great%20on%20the%20field%2C%20he%20is%20batting%20longer%20hours%2C%20and%20he%20has%20trained%20really%20hard.%20Our%20S%26amp%3BCs%20(strength%20and%20conditioning)%20and%20physios%20have%20worked%20hard%20with%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMentally%2C%20to%20have%20a%20mindset%20like%20that%20after%20being%20rejected%20or%20not%20getting%20his%20due%2C%20he%20has%20taken%20it%20very%20positively.%20Even%20when%20he%20talks%20about%20it%2C%20he%20is%20not%20negative%2C%20he%20understands%20he%20needs%20to%20go%20back%20and%20do%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENayar%20said%20that%20Iyer's%20mindset%20is%20to%20score%20runs%20no%20matter%20for%20which%20team%20he%20plays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20looks%20to%20score%20runs%2C%20it%20(his%20setbacks)%20has%20affected%20him%20but%20the%20way%20he%20has%20handled%20it%2C%20kudos%20to%20him%20because%20I%20can%20imagine%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20reacting%20very%20differently%20than%20he%20has%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20coach%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20bonding%20between%20mentor%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20bowling%20all-rounder%20Sunil%20Narine%2C%20Nayar%20said%20that%20the%20bond%20between%20these%20two%20is%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%26quot%3B%20which%20gets%20reflected%20in%20his%20hard-hitting%20batting%20at%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20very%20personal%20bond.%20It%20is%20best%20understood%20by%20those%20two%20people.%20It%20is%20not%20necessarily%20a%20coaching%20thing%2C%20it%20can%20also%20be%20a%20trust%20thing.%20Sometimes%20just%20having%20someone%20in%20the%20dugout%20and%20having%20that%20aura%20around%20you%20can%20have%20a%20positive%20effect%20on%20the%20player.%20There%20can%20be%20many%20other%20things%2C%20like%20Gauti%20telling%20him%20to%20go%20there%20and%20play%20with%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%