5%2C000%20residents%20south%20of%20Oklahoma%20City.%20Four%20people%20were%20killed%20across%20the%20state%2C%20including%20a%20woman%20who%20was%20in%20a%20bar%20near%20the%20newspaper's%20offices.%20Kathy%20John's%20husband%2C%20James%20John%2C%20joined%20the%20staff%20in%201968%2C%20after%20his%20father%20ran%20it%20for%2027%20years.%20Together%2C%20the%20pair%20have%20been%20covering%20Sulphur%2C%20the%20county%20seat%2C%20for%20more%20than%2050%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fa-tornado-hit-an-oklahoma-newsroom-built-in-the-1920s-the-damage-isnt-stopping-the-presses%2Farticleshow%2F109805263.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fa-tornado-hit-an-oklahoma-newsroom-built-in-the-1920s-the-damage-isnt-stopping-the-presses%2Famp_articleshow%2F109805263.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fa-tornado-hit-an-oklahoma-newsroom-built-in-the-1920s-the-damage-isnt-stopping-the-presses%2Famp_articleshow%2F109805263.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Highways%20Authority%20Planning%20To%20Build%20Self-Healing%20Roads%20In%20India%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI)%20is%20planning%20to%20introduce%20a%20revolutionary%20technology%20for%20road%20maintenance%20in%20the%20country.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDDNewsHindi%2Fstatus%2F1786016539545633004%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDD%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20This%20technology%20will%20enable%20a%20road%20to%20'repair'%20itself%20using%20a%20new%20type%20of%20asphalt.%20This%20material%20will%20be%20infused%20with%20steel%20fibre%20and%20bitumen.%20If%20a%20gap%20emerges%20on%20the%20road%2C%20the%20bitumen%20will%20spread%20to%20cover%20it%20and%20along%20with%20steel%20threads%2C%20fill%20the%20potholes.%20NHAI%20official%20say%20it%20will%20fix%20the%20persistent%20problem%20of%20potholes%2C%20a%20major%20contributor%20to%20road%20accidents%20and%20fatalities%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%2C%20however%2C%20not%20known%20how%20long%20the%20asphalt%20will%20take%20to%20cover%20and%20'repair'%20a%20pothole%20or%20gap%20in%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20considering%20ingenious%20and%20unconventional%20methods%20to%20improve%20durability%20and%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20potholes%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Ftransportation%2Froadways%2Fself-healing-roads-may-soon-be-a-reality-nhai%2Farticleshow%2F109671277.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20government%20will%20undertake%20cost-benefit%20analysis%20of%20the%20project%20before%20giving%20a%20go-ahead.%20NHAI%20is%20confident%20that%20the%20new%20technology%20will%20increase%20the%20lifespan%20of%20roads%20and%20minimise%20traffic%20disruption%20caused%20by%20potholes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsphalt%20is%20a%20sustainable%20paving%20material%20used%20for%20constructing%20pavements%20and%20highways%2C%20along%20with%20airport%20runways%2C%20parking%20lots%20and%20driveways.%20Asphalt%20ultimately%20speeds%20construction%2C%20is%20environmentally%20friendly%2C%20and%20provides%20a%20smooth%20and%20quiet%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20made%20by%20a%20mixture%20of%20aggregates%2C%20binder%20and%20filler.%20Aggregates%20are%20mixed%20with%20bitumen%20to%20create%20a%20durable%20and%20reliable%20mixture.%20Specialised%20trucks%20or%20transporters%20deliver%20the%20hot%20asphalt%20mixture%20to%20the%20desired%20location%2C%20where%20it%20is%20spread%20and%20compacted%20using%20heavy%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20bitumen%20deteriorates%2C%20leading%20to%20erosion%20of%20the%20asphalt%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20cracks%2C%20which%20eventually%20evolve%20into%20hazardous%20potholes.%20The%20new%20technology%20aims%20to%20tackle%20this%20degradation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENHAI%20is%20a%20government%20agency%20responsible%20for%20construction%20and%20management%20of%20road%20network%20of%20national%20highways%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714714680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F9q9l6rvg_india-national-highways-india-expressways-ani_625x300_27_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhighways-authority-planning-to-build-self-healing-roads-in-india-report-5577951%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20will%20undertake%20cost-benefit%20analysis%20of%20the%20project%20before%20giving%20a%20go-ahead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhighways-authority-planning-to-build-self-healing-roads-in-india-report-5577951%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhighways-authority-planning-to-build-self-healing-roads-in-india-report-5577951%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhighways-authority-planning-to-build-self-healing-roads-in-india-report-5577951%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20says%20it%20downs%20six%20Ukraine-launched%20drones%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714714477000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109805184%2Cimgsize-20696.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-says-it-downs-six-ukraine-launched-drones%2Farticleshow%2F109805184.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatim