path%20for%20me%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3E1.%20Well-earned%20wisdom%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20built%20a%20successful%20career%20in%20content%20and%20visited%20dozens%20of%20countries%20in%20my%20first%20four%20decades%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20bring%20a%20lot%20of%20life%20experience%20to%20motherhood%20without%20it%20defining%20who%20I%20am.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBack%20in%20my%2020s%2C%20I%20lived%20with%20roommates%20in%20New%20York%20and%20was%20more%20worried%20about%20making%20weekend%20plans%20than%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoula-advice-things-pregnant-people-should-know-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewriting%20a%20birth%20plan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20also%20frequently%20had%20to%20stay%20late%20at%20the%20office%20when%20publication%20deadlines%20loomed.%20I%20didn't%20envy%20coworkers%20with%20families%20waiting%20at%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20these%20years%2C%20I%20learned%20many%20valuable%20lessons%20that%20I%20still%20use%20today%20as%20a%20mom%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-remarried-after-divorce-raising-sons-blended-family-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eblended%20family%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20my%20husband%20and%20our%20three%20boys.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20surrounding%20myself%20with%20positive%20people%20translates%20to%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20supportive%20environment%20for%20our%20kids.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20countless%20nights%20spent%20burning%20the%20midnight%20oil%20for%20work%20taught%20me%20the%20importance%20of%20prioritizing%20sleep%20and%20creating%20a%20healthy%20routine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20talk%20as%20a%20family%20about%20different%20cultures%20or%20customs%2C%20I%20can%20draw%20from%20my%20travel%20experiences%20to%20encourage%20our%20boys%20to%20be%20open-minded.%20Being%20laid%20off%20from%20my%20job%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20before%20having%20kids%20has%20instilled%20in%20me%20both%20humility%20and%20resilience%20%E2%80%94%20two%20traits%20I%20actively%20try%20to%20nurture%20in%20our%20children.%20Neither%20my%20husband%20nor%20I%20want%20to%20raise%20entitled%20kids%2C%20and%20fostering%20gratitude%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20last%20lesson%20hit%20home%20when%20I%20lost%20my%20dad%20the%20year%20before%20I%20had%20my%20son.%20It%20has%20made%20me%20deeply%20appreciative%20of%20spending%20quality%20time%20with%20family%2C%20something%20my%20husband%20is%20just%20as%20passionate%20about.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20%3Cspan%3EMore%20stability%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-kids-cost-raising-child-inflation-childcare-tax-exemptions-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20calculated%20the%20annual%20cost%20of%20caring%20for%20one%20young%20child%20in%20the%20US%20at%20nearly%20%2426%2C000%2C%20including%20housing%2C%20food%2C%20clothes%2C%20transportation%2C%20childcare%2C%20healthcare%20insurance%20premiums%2C%20and%20other%20expenses.%20That%20figure%20is%20about%20the%20same%20amount%20I%20made%20in%20my%20first%20job%20as%20an%20editorial%20assistant%20when%20I%20was%2021.%20Having%20a%20baby%20back%20then%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20the%20cost%20were%20only%20half%20the%20amount%20it%20is%20now%20%E2%80%94%20would%20have%20been%20out%20of%20the%20question%2C%20financially%20speaking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20got%20pregnant%2015%20years%20later%2C%20after%20also%20getting%20married%20and%20factoring%20in%20my%20then-husband's%20income%2C%20I%20was%20in%20a%20much%20better%20position%20to%20raise%20a%20child.%20While%20money%20can't%20buy%20happiness%2C%20it%20can%20give%20you%20more%20stability.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221424%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20and%20woman%20getting%20married%20with%20scenic%20Colorado%20backdrop%2C%20three%20kids%20are%20watching%20nearby%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66345dddec0c69656900979d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221068%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20the%20author%20and%20her%20husband's%20wedding%20day%20at%20a%20scenic%20location%20in%20Colorado%2C%20their%20three%20sons%20were%20the%20only%20invited%20guests.%3Cp%3ESara%20Lyle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20%3Cspan%3EStaying%20young-ish%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20being%20a%20mom%20of%20three%20keeps%20me%20active%20and%20engaged.%20From%20running%20alongside%20the%20boys%20in%20a%20fun-but-messy%20%26quot%3Bmudder%26quot%3B%20race%20to%20deciphering%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-slang-words-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elatest%20slang%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20like%20%26quot%3Brizz%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bbussin%26quot%3B%20over%20dinner%2C%20it's%20a%20constant%20adventure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStaying%20healthy%20and%20involved%20in%20your%20kids'%20lives%20is%20likely%20important%20to%20parents%20of%20all%20ages.%20But%20for%20me%2C%20it%20feels%20even%20more%20significant.%20In%20my%2020s%20and%2030s%2C%20running%20half-marathons%20and%20keeping%20up%20with%20pop%20culture%20came%20easily.%20Now%2C%20it%20takes%20a%20little%20more%20effort%2C%20but%20the%20payoff%20is%20greater%20by%20being%20fully%20present%20for%20my%20kids.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELooking%20even%20further%20ahead%2C%20I'm%20conscious%20of%20wanting%20to%20be%20around%20when%20our%20kids%20have%20kids%2C%20like%20some%20of%20my%20forty-something%