%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20alliance%20said%20this%20includes%20sabotage%2C%20acts%20of%20violence%2C%20and%20disinformation%20campaigns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20North%20Atlantic%20Council%20said%20it%C2%A0%26quot%3Bwill%20act%20individually%20and%20collectively%20to%20address%20these%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20North%20Atlantic%20Treaty%20Organization%20on%20Thursday%20singled%20out%20Russia%20in%20a%20statement%20condemning%20%26quot%3Brecent%20malign%20activities%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20member%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20includes%20sabotage%2C%20acts%20of%20violence%2C%20cyber%20and%20electronic%20interference%2C%20disinformation%20campaigns%2C%20and%20other%20hybrid%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nato.int%2Fcps%2Fen%2Fnatohq%2Fofficial_texts_225230.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENorth%20Atlantic%20Council%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20council%20said%20it%20made%20its%20statement%20amid%20investigations%20and%20charges%20against%20people%20accused%20of%20hostile%20state%20activity%20in%20Czechia%2C%20Estonia%2C%20Germany%2C%20Latvia%2C%20Lithuania%2C%20Poland%2C%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20treaty%20organization%20said%20these%20individuals'%20actions%20were%20part%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Bintensifying%20campaign%20of%20activities%26quot%3B%20carried%20out%20by%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20act%20individually%20and%20collectively%20to%20address%20these%20actions%2C%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20coordinate%20closely%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20condemned%20Russia%20for%20its%20accused%20behavior%20and%20called%20on%20Moscow%20to%20uphold%20international%20obligations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussia's%20actions%20will%20not%20deter%20Allies%20from%20continuing%20to%20support%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20Febru